17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 3-101, as
18 amended by Section 2, Chapter 329, O.S.L. 2023 (26 O.S. Supp. 2024,
19 Section 3-101), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 3-101. A. No election required to be conducted by any
21 county election board shall be scheduled for a day other than
22 Tuesday.
23 B. Except as otherwise provided by law, no regular or special
24 election to fill an elective office for any purpose shall be held by
